This paper is likely to belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) category as it deals with the balance of exploration versus exploitation in evolutionary computation. It could also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) categories as these fields are closely related to evolutionary computation. The paper's focus on adaptive control suggests it could also belong to the Systems and Control (cs.SY) category. Finally, the paper's investigation of search strategies suggests it could also belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE) category.
